WEBVTT

00:04.841 --> 00:07.330
Whenever I'm around you...

00:08.710 --> 00:10.951
...I go home a little bit.

00:12.975 --> 00:15.390
There's just something about you...

00:16.575 --> 00:19.250
...where the pieces all fit.

00:21.014 --> 00:24.679
There's a lightness that surrounds you...

00:25.555 --> 00:28.910
...and it guides me like a star.

00:29.645 --> 00:32.691
Oh, I am who I am...

00:33.960 --> 00:37.216
...because you are who you are.

00:38.249 --> 00:42.110
Truth is this and don't forget,...

00:42.345 --> 00:49.400
...that my world's better 'cause you're in it.

00:54.940 --> 00:58.605
Oh, I am who I am...

00:59.867 --> 01:03.470
...because you are who you are.

